      <div class="msgContentFrame">Absolutely. Use Sac I and Cure I in sequence if you need a healing boost. Only time Sac II and Cure II need to be broken out is if I's cannot keep up with mob damage. In any situation where I's are sufficient they should be preferred. Furthermore, conjurers may want to use Sac I more than Cure I as you get double proc on regen buff; it also heals for less so you have more chance of full SP gain. <br /> <br />System is all backwards and unintuitive but this is the way healers should be EXPing at this time.</div>
